                              card precfg parsing.  Some cases need to shut down the lc first  then change the configuration or change the pic card  Eg.
                              if the card is pre-configured as RPHY with the command  'card <slot_num>/0 cBR-CCAP-LC-40G r-phy'  but a rf-pic card was inserted
